OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FThe parents of a woman who was found
OL,7,Fdead and in an "almost skeletal" state
OL,8,Fby paramedics have been jailed for
OL,9,Fcausing the death of their vulnerable
OL,10,Fdaughter.
OL,12,FSteffie Davies, 32, who rarely left
OL,13,Fthe family home in Wrexham due to
OL,14,Fanxiety, was found dead and in May
OL,15,F2023.
OL,17,FHer parents, Alan and Bernita Davies,
OL,18,Fboth 60, were each sentenced to eight
OL,19,Fyears imprisonment at a hearing at
OL,20,FMold Crown Court today (Thursday, 19
OL,21,FMarch).
OL,26,@oD@`O]|D@Xpm}D@Fpn
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/11
