CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774098665
OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FSentencing, Mrs Justice Stacey said:
OL,7,F"There is no evidence of her ever
OL,8,Fhaving been shown love and affection.
OL,10,F"Instead, she was verbally abused by
OL,11,Fyou and you showed complete
OL,12,Findifference to her suffering."
OL,14,FThe two-day hearing was told Ms Davies
OL,15,Fwas found with dirty, matted hair, had
OL,16,Fsuspected fungal infections on her
OL,17,Fskin and was "almost skeletal", with
OL,18,Fpressure sores and joint contractures
OL,19,Fwhich would have prevented her from
OL,20,Feating or drinking without assistance.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUtD@_O]yD@NOUyD@^O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/11
