PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774098665
OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FAndrew Jones KC, prosecuting, said she
OL,7,Fweighed five stone, nine pounds at the
OL,8,Ftime of her death and was five foot
OL,9,Fseven inches.
OL,11,FPhotos of her injuries were ruled too
OL,12,Fdistressing to be shown in court.
OL,14,FBernita Davies was described as the
OL,15,F"mother from hell" by a neighbour
OL,16,Fbecause of the way she shouted at her
OL,17,Fthree children when they were young.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@RO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
