OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774098665
OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FThe last time Ms Davies was seen
OL,7,Foutside the house, in 2017, her mother
OL,8,Fwas seen shouting at her and calling
OL,9,Fher "stupid", the court heard.
OL,11,FAlan Davies, a factory worker, told
OL,12,Fparamedics his daughter had not been
OL,13,Fout of bed for 12 months before she
OL,14,Fdied and her younger brother said in
OL,15,FDecember 2022 Ms Davies was bed-bound
OL,16,Fand too weak to open a box of
OL,17,Fchocolates he had given her for
OL,18,FChristmas.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@LO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G4/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774098665
OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FMrs Justice Stacey said: "As she lay
OL,7,Fin extreme pain, wasting away and
OL,8,Fdying in the front room of the house,
OL,9,Fyou both carried on with your lives,
OL,10,Fgoing to work, feeding yourselves from
OL,11,Fthe well-stocked fridge-freezer and
OL,12,Flarder, while she lay starving and
OL,13,Funable to feed herself in the next
OL,14,Fdoor room. You simply ignored her."
OL,26,@nD@ZOUvD@cO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774098665
OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FText messages between mother and
OL,7,Fdaughter showed Bernita Davies
OL,8,F"ghosting" her, the judge said, and
OL,9,Fthere was no reply to a message from
OL,10,FAugust 2022 in which Ms Davies asked
OL,11,Ffor something to settle her stomach or
OL,12,Fprotein drinks.
OL,14,FMrs Justice Stacey said she did not
OL,15,Faccept there was evidence of "genuine
OL,16,Fremorse", adding that pre-sentence
OL,17,Freports for the couple showed victim-
OL,18,Fblaming and self-pity.
OL,26,@pD@AOUpD@JO]wD@^OUxD@HO]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
