OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774098665
OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FShe said Ms Davies did not have
OL,7,Funderlying health problems before her
OL,8,Fdeath, adding: "It was you, her
OL,9,Fparents, you were the problem."
OL,11,FBernita Davies, a supermarket
OL,12,Fsupervisor, called paramedics at
OL,13,F8:30am on 26 May 2023 to report her
OL,14,Fdaughter's death and later told
OL,15,Fofficers she had checked on her the
OL,16,Fprevious day and found her sleeping.
OL,18,FBut the court heard Ms Davies was
OL,19,Flikely to have been dead for several
OL,20,Fdays by the time emergency services
OL,21,Fwere called.
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@_O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774098665
OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FIn a statement, Ms Davies' older
OL,7,Fsister said she had shown potential at
OL,8,Fcollege, where she studied animal
OL,9,Fcare, but her anxiety grew as she got
OL,10,Folder and she found it hard to leave
OL,11,Fthe house.
OL,13,FThe woman, who was not named in court
OL,14,Fand had been estranged from their
OL,15,Fparents for a number of years, said:
OL,16,F"With the right support and
OL,17,Fencouragement from my mum and dad she
OL,18,Fcould have done so much with her life.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G8/11
OL,2,W+.-'*%/"-$+,(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774098665
OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,F"Instead she was left to fade into
OL,7,Finsignificance in the most inhumane
OL,8,Fway possible. No sentence could ever
OL,9,Fbe enough to atone for that."
OL,11,FThe Davies', who both made no comment
OL,12,Fin police interviews, were initially
OL,13,Fcharged with gross negligence
OL,14,Fmanslaughter but guilty pleas to the
OL,15,Flesser charge of causing or allowing
OL,16,Ftheir daughter's death were accepted
OL,17,Fearlier this year.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@]O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/11
