OL,24,ANext Page BWales News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,466,460,260,120,000,100
PN,46510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1774098665
OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FSenior investigating officer Detective
OL,7,FSuperintendent Sarah-Jayne Williams
OL,8,Fsaid: "It is difficult to comprehend
OL,9,Fthat a once fit and healthy woman had
OL,10,Fbeen able to deteriorate to the point
OL,11,Fof death with no intervention from her
OL,12,Fmother and father, who she resided
OL,13,Fwith at the time and would have been
OL,14,Ffully aware of her deteriorating
OL,15,Fcondition.
OL,17,F"Both Alan and Bernita Davies have
OL,18,Facknowledged the level of care they
OL,19,Fprovided for their daughter was
OL,20,Fwoefully inadequate, which led to her
OL,21,Ftragic and unavoidable death."
OL,26,@pD@GOUyD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G10/11
