OL,3,CParents jailed after daughter died in
OL,4,C'almost skeletal' state at home
OL,6,FA spokesman for Wrexham Council said:
OL,7,F"Steffie Davies was not known to
OL,8,Fsocial services in Wrexham, however we
OL,9,Fwill be liaising with North Wales
OL,10,FSafeguarding Board in order to
OL,11,Fconsider if this case meets the
OL,12,Fthreshold for a review."
